DESCRIPTION:
------------
This configuration works if you store you music as follow:
 - Like the "nospace" configuration but with only lowacase 
    - For all folder and file names


TREE STRUCTURE:
---------------
example-tree/
|-- alice
|   |-- 2000.first_album
|   |   |-- 01.track_one.mp3
|   |   |-- 02.track_two.mp3
|   |   |-- 03.track_three.mp3
|   |   |-- cover.jpg
|   |   `-- playlist.m3u
|   `-- 2001.second_album
|       |-- 01.track_one.mp3
|       |-- 02.track_two.mp3
|       |-- 03.track_three.mp3
|       |-- cover.jpg
|       `-- playlist.m3u
`-- bob
    `-- the_album
        |-- 01.track_one.mp3
        |-- 02.track_two.mp3
        `-- 03.track_three.mp3

